International Users


Please note that we may transfer, store and process your personal information outside the country you live in. Your personal information is also processed by staff and third party service providers and partners in these countries.


If we transfer your personal information out of Europe, we will rely on recognized transfer mechanisms like the European Commission's Standard Contractual Clauses, or any equivalent contracts issued by the relevant competent authority of the UK, as relevant, unless the data transfer is to a country that has been determined to provide an adequate level of protection.


Contact


Should you have any questions about our privacy practices or this Privacy Policy, or if you would like to exercise any of the rights available to you, please call or email us at info@thebioedge.co or contact us at 3 Bridgeway, Cape Town, WC, 7441, ZA.

Versandrichtlinie

Bestellungen werden innerhalb von 1-3 Werktagen bearbeitet und versandt.


Sobald Ihre Bestellung versandt wurde, kommt sie in der Regel innerhalb von 6-8 Werktagen an.


Sie erhalten eine Sendungsverfolgungsnummer per E-Mail, sobald Ihre Bestellung versandt wurde.


Fragen zu Ihrer Bestellung oder unseren Lieferzeiten richten Sie bitte hier an uns.
